    "description": {
      "value": "<p>At 1st level, you can touch a weapon or up to 50 pieces of ammunition as a <em>standard action</em>, giving it the <em>frost</em> property for a number of rounds equal to 1/2 your sorcerer level (minimum 1). At 9th level, you can confer the <em>icy burst</em> property instead, but the duration of the power is halved. You can use this ability a number of times per day equal to 3 + your <em>Charisma</em> modifier.</p>"
